'''Bozzie''' was an [[Ewok/Legends|Ewok]] from the forest moon of [[Endor/Legends|Endor]]. She was the sister or sister-in-law of [[Chief/Legends|Chief]] [[Chirpa/Legends|Chirpa]], mother of [[Paploo/Legends|Paploo]] and the aunt of [[Princess/Legends|Princess]] [[Kneesaa a Jari Kintaka/Legends|Kneesaa]] and [[Asha/Legends|Asha]]. She had a matronly manner, but at times, she could be bossy and domineering.

She particularly had difficulties with [[Wicket Wystri Warrick/Legends|Wicket Wystri Warrick]] who inadvertently antagonized her on repeated occasions. When Wicket personally saved both her and her [[Soul Tree]] from a massive forest fire, the pair reconciled. However, that new understanding did not prevent her from assuming that the young Ewok had misused village trade goods for a personal purchase upon returning from an expedition until she was reassured that Wicket had used his own trade items for it.

{{Char-stub}}

